NK_TUSC2_STRESS_IEG
# Curated 44-gene Stress / IEG / antioxidant / UPR set used for volcano label
# colouring in the volcano panels.
# Sources: MSigDB Hallmark TNF-alpha Signaling via NF-kB, Hallmark UV
# Response Up, GO:0006950 (response to stress). Antioxidant subset
# (PRDX*, SOD1, GPX1, TXNRD1, TXNIP, GSTP1) is included here, not in
# metabolism, as a distinct biological axis rather than part of OXPHOS.
#
# AP-1 / early-response
