# Additional markers (Crinier / Tang / Collins):
# MAFF — stressed CD56bright TF (hypoxia/ROS axis)
# KLF2 — Crinier 2018 homeostatic / S1PR5 / migration TF
# KLF6 — Tang 2023 elevated in TaNK dysfunction; Crinier homeostatic TF
# EOMES — assigned to stress here (not exhaustion). Collins/Zhang 2021 use EOMES
#   as the NK maturation rheostat, not a dysfunction marker. The CD8 config also
#   places EOMES in PROGENITOR (Intlekofer 2005; Zheng 2021), not exhaustion —
#   both pipelines agree EOMES is never terminal-exhaustion.
MAFF
KLF2
KLF6
EOMES
